    "We report accuracy.",
    "TruthfulQA TruthfulQA (Lin et al., 2021) assesses a model's ability to avoid common misconceptions by answering 818 questions to which humans often respond incorrectly.",
    "We report rouge1_acc, which measures the proportion of answers classified as truthful ToxiGen ToxiGen (Hartvigsen et al., 2022) evaluates bias and toxicity in LLM completions.",
    "It contains toxic and benign statements across 13 minority groups.",
    "We report acc_norm."
  ],
